---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Note from "../../components/Note.astro";
const title = "motors & drivers — ecute.club";
---
<BaseLayout {title}>
  <article class="container">
    <h1>motors &amp; drivers</h1>
    <p>a motor turns electrical power into motion. most need more current than MCU pins can supply → use a transistor or motor driver.</p>

    <h2>types</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>DC motor:</strong> speed with PWM; direction with H-bridge.</li>
      <li><strong>servo:</strong> controls angle via signal; has its own driver inside.</li>
      <li><strong>stepper:</strong> moves in steps; needs a stepper driver.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="diagram" role="img" aria-label="NPN low-side motor driver with flyback diode">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 560 170" width="100%" height="auto">
        <rect x="0" y="0" width="560" height="170" rx="16" fill="var(--card)"/>
        <text x="36" y="34" class="mono">uC pin</text>
        <line x1="80" y1="30" x2="180" y2="30" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        <rect x="180" y="20" width="24" height="20" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        <text x="176" y="16" class="mono mini">1k</text>
        <line x1="204" y1="30" x2="260" y2="30" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        <circle cx="260" cy="60" r="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        <text x="252" y="64" class="mono mini">NPN</text>
        <line x1="260" y1="44" x2="260" y2="30" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="260" y1="76" x2="260" y2="120" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="260" y1="44" x2="360" y2="44" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        <rect x="360" y="34" width="36" height="20" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        <text x="362" y="28" class="mono mini">motor</text>
        <line x1="396" y1="44" x2="440" y2="44" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        <text x="448" y="48" class="mono">+V</text>
        <polygon points="360,68 385,52 385,84" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="385" y1="52" x2="385" y2="84" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        <text x="392" y="78" class="mono mini">diode</text>
        <line x1="40" y1="140" x2="520" y2="140" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        <text x="18" y="144" class="mono">0V</text>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <p class="example">bigger loads → MOSFET or dedicated driver; add a fuse for safety.</p>

    <Note variant="care">choose a driver rated above stall current; add bulk caps close to the driver and protect with flybacks where needed.</Note>

     <h2>servo &amp; stepper quickies</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>servo:</strong> 5 V power + control pulse every ~20 ms (use a servo library).</li>
      <li><strong>stepper:</strong> needs a stepper driver (A4988, TMC) and distinct supply current.</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
